2ï¸âƒ£ FUNCTION CALL & RETURN using stact discipline== apne program ne FUNCTION call kita FUNCTION de ADRESS te PROGRAM ne JUMP kita..RETURN ADDRESS mtlb jithe program ne FUNCTION CALL to bad vapas aona mtlb NEXT INSTRUCTION da ADDRESS STACK te PUSH hogya
