ğŸ”´ğŸ”´jdo v INTERRUPT occur hundia ta CPU ek PREDETERMINED location's te JUMP krda & these PREDETERMINED location's are called INTERRUPT VECTORS
ğŸ”´ğŸ”´âœ”ï¸WHAT ARE INTERRUPT VECTORS ? ğŸ”´ğŸ”´
